@@TJvCheckListBox.GetChecked
Description:
Call this method to retrieve all checked elements of the list.
If you have stored datas in the associated object (Objects[]), they are also present in this list.

================================================================
@@TJvCheckListBox.GetUnChecked
Description:
Call this method to retrieve all non checked elements of the list.
If you have stored datas in the associated object (Objects[]), they are also present in this list.

================================================================
@@TJvCheckListBox.InvertCheck
Description:
Call this method to check all elements of the list. All checked items are unchecked and others are checked.

================================================================
@@TJvCheckListBox.InvertSelection
Description:
Call this method to invert the selection of the elements.
If the MultiSelect property is false, this method has no effect! After calling this method, all selected elements aren't anymore, and all elements non selected are now selected.

